                  <dd/>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry>
                  <dt><uicontrol>Add Local Catalog</uicontrol></dt>
                  <dd>Adds a catalog to the selected library. By default, only the root-library has
                    a catalog, and all models are stored there.</dd>
                </dlentry>
