                  <dd/>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-working-with-databases/copy-location">
                  <dt/>
                  <dd/>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry>
                  <dt><uicontrol>Add AS model</uicontrol></dt>
                  <dd>Allows you to add an XML schema to the selected XML resource.</dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry>
                  <dt><uicontrol>Set AS model</uicontrol></dt>
                  <dd>Allows you to set an active AS model for the selected XML resource.</dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry>
                  <dt><uicontrol>Clear AS model</uicontrol></dt>
                  <dd>Allows you to clear the active AS model of the selected XML resource.</dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry>
                  <dt><uicontrol>Properties</uicontrol></dt>
                  <dd>Displays the resource properties. Available only for XML resources.</dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry>
                  <dt><uicontrol>Set Default Schema</uicontrol></dt>
                  <dd>Allows you to set the selected DTD to be used as default for parsing. The
                    action is available only for DTD.</dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry>
                  <dt><uicontrol>Clear Default Schema</uicontrol></dt>
                  <dd>Allows you to unset the selected DTD. The action is available only if the
                    selected DTD is the current default to be used for parsing.</dd>
                </dlentry>
